      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  FillDocumentVisitor

      class  GeneralVariableListerVisitor
      Lists the variables inside a general expression (no pre-conditions).
      class  GreatestSubFormulaListerVisitor
      Gets the set biggest of none-ctl sub formulae of a general expression (no pre-conditions).
      class  PreFixStringVisitor
      Visitor for printing an AbstractExpression in a formatted way.

      Lists all the process Indices used in a given expression.
      class  SetValuationVisitor
      Sets the valuation of an AbstractExpression and all of its children, children of children, etc..
      class  VariableListerVisitor
      This visitor lists the variables within an AndExpression, variables are listed in order and grouped by clause.
